+# Same-Student Cross-Surface Parity Report
+
+Pass: `same-student-cross-surface-parity-pass`
+Date: `2026-04-16`
+Context: `live` with local forensic reconciliation
+Model / provider / account: `gpt-5.4 / native-codex / native-codex-session`
